 A = \left( \begin{array}{ccc} k & 0 & 1 \\ 0 & 1 & 0 \\ 1 & 0 & k \end{array} \right) 
k
A = A^{-1}
A\cdot A{}{}{}
A = A^{-1} \Rightarrow A^2 = I
A^2
I
A^2=\left[ \begin{array}{ccc} k^2+1 & 0 & 2k \\ 0 & 1 & 0 \\ 2k & 0 & k^2+1 \end{array} \right]\stackrel{!}=\left[ \begin{array}{ccc} 1 & 0 & 0 \\ 0 & 1 & 0 \\0 & 0 & 1\end{array} \right]
